name: $cancel
desc: Retrieve selected or all queued resources or messages.

name: $poll
desc: Release any reserved funds or material obligations associated with a resource. For example, any unused but reserved funds or treatment allowance associated with a preauthorization once treatment is complete.

name: $release
desc: Indication that the processing of a resource, such as a claim, for some or all of the required work is now being requested.

name: $reprocess
desc: Check on the processing status of a resource such as the adjudication of a claim.
